---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-surface border-t border-border mt-20">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-text mb-3">Orange County BLS Training</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          AHA-authorized BLS and ACLS training in Orange County, CA. Hybrid format — online coursework plus in-person skills check.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-text mb-3">Certification</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          AHA BLS Provider and ACLS Provider eCards are valid for 2 years from date of issue.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 pt-6 border-t border-border text-center text-xs text-text-muted space-y-2">
      <p>
        &copy; {currentYear} Orange County BLS Training. All rights reserved.
      </p>
      <p>
        This site is operated by an American Heart Association authorized instructor. AHA and American Heart Association are trademarks of the American Heart Association, Inc.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
